    <stitle>FULL POWER HYDRAULIC ABS BRAKE SYSTEM - SPECIAL TOOLS - COMMON TOOLS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>COMMON TOOLS</title>
        <para>The tools in the following list can be obtained from local sources.</para>
        <randlist type="bullet">
            <item>
                <para>Strap wrench head for torque wrench - must be capable of gripping the accumulator.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>1 3/16 inch extra deep, thin-walled, deep well socket, such as ZTSE4781 (or equivalent).</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Pressurized brake bleeding system</para>
                <randlist type="bullet">
                    <item>
                        <para>Air-over-fluid bleeding systems require a regulator/filter, such as ZTSE4757-1 (or
                            equivalent). Refer to
                            <hotlnk document="s04048_HL04048801.xml" xrefid="f0404883">FIGURE 80</hotlnk>.
                        </para>
                    </item>
                </randlist>
            </item>
        </randlist>
    </svcproc>
